p: Thirteen variants were successfully imputed from the four genotyping platforms in the 23andMe cohort with the average and minimum imputation quality across all batches (avg.rsqr and min.rsqr) ranging from 0.96 to 1 for avg.rsqr (average across 13 variants was 0.995) and 0.86 to 1 for min.rsqr (average = 0.982) ( S1 Table).
